Export
------

The creation of a collision model for use with a map is done
automatically by the engine upon compile with the
[dmap](Dmap_%28console_command%29 "Dmap (console command)") console
command.

To create a collision model for use with a moveable physics object, from
within the level editor, you must select the brushes and/or model. Then
click **Selection \> Export \> to CM** .

From this point the .CM file must be named and placed in the same
directory as the map or model.

